replies.author: lliiooll
replies.txt_content:
打开config/forge.cfg
将

B:removeErroringEntities=false

B:removeErroringTileEntities=false复制代码
设置为
B:removeErroringEntities=true

B:removeErroringTileEntities=true复制代码重启即可
